# 🧠 Primer Omnichain Assistant

A unified app that combines:
- A FastAPI web interface
- A Telegram bot
- Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) via Qdrant
- Thread generation using OpenAI

## 🛠️ Features

- 🔍 Ask questions and get context-aware answers from LayerZero docs
- 🧵 Generate Twitter-style threads on any topic
- 💬 Works via both web UI and Telegram
- 🔒 Rate-limited to avoid spam

---

## 🚀 Local Setup

1. **Clone the repo**:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/primer_omnichain_assistant.git
cd primer_omnichain_assistant

install dependencies

```pip install -r requirements.txt```

create env file

```cp .env.sample .env
# Then fill in your actual keys
```

Run the Project: ```chmod +x start.sh
./start.sh```

 API & Bot
FastAPI: http://localhost:8000

Telegram Bot: responds to /start, /thread [topic], or any message